{"tid":2139740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【美中冷戰】侵侵批准微軟收購TikTok 只限45日","createTime":"2020-08-04T13:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T13:11:54.000Z","uid":293677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2b1840b83f7ba433a28db86b30a6e0139878e9b","tid":2139740,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"2020-08-04 19:56:23<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/08/04/php8cYXG6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F08%2F04%2Fphp8cYXG6.jpg&h=fff923ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"xx-large\">美國總統川普一度決定封殺中國短影音平台「抖音」海外版TikTok，不過在與微軟（Microsoft）會談後，決定對微軟收購TikTok的談判「開綠燈」，但只限45天；川普也稱，如果TikTok最後成功被美企收購，美國政府有權從中抽成，而且應該占收購價「相當大一部分」。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n綜合外媒報導，川普表示，交易雙方原本都無權進行收購談判，這是我「准許促成的」，如果沒有我根本不可能發生，所以不管最後是微軟還是TikTok要支付，美國政府從收購金中抽取一筆為數不小的費用「相當合情合理」；川普還將抽成比喻成「房東跟房客的關係」。他強調，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">TikTok利用美國獲得巨大的成功，「難道不用付點房租嗎？」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《彭博社》指出，綜觀美國近代歷史，美國政府要從一間沒有持有股份的公司抽取一筆額外的費用是「絕無僅有」，即便是美國海外投資委員會（CFIUS）向提出收購案進行審查的外商收取費用，金額也不會超過上限30萬美元（約新台幣881萬元），不符合川普的說法；美國三大律師事務所之一的歐華律師事務所（DLA Piper）律師克萊因（Nicholas Klein）也認為，美國政府無權透過CFIUS收取任何費用。<br />\n<br />\n美國麻省理工學院發行的科技報刊《麻省理工科技評論》（MIT Technology Review）記者夏洛特&middot;吉（Charlotte Jee）認為，讓微軟收購TikTok美國業務的行為「匪夷所思」，美國國會上週才審查4間科技公司是否有壟斷市場，結果現在川普竟意圖讓其中一間公司「變得更大」。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">美國強硬要求TikTok得在9月15日退出美國市場，除非將美國業務分割出售給美國企業</span></span>，以防止中國政府有機會染指美國人的個資，不過據稱微軟除了與TikTok洽談收購美國業務的經營權外，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">同時也要求收購加拿大、澳洲以及紐西蘭等「五眼聯盟」成員國的業務。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3249563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3249563&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4YdwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=7dc759dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3249563&h=1b43f6e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3249563</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319b3323b3a15536ba0f357a3033db52dcef9a60","tid":2139740,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"抖音侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a44a8cd1e532aa6f5abb6c7589315a3434057ed","tid":2139740,"uid":296345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"Tik Tok Trump! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTik Tok Trump! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffeb969c3c4b1985ef7dc206614b4d5b8938285","tid":2139740,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"不過，咁講好放生feel <br />\n如果政府收唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10027471792dad3476c23eb7d2109e435886c92","tid":2139740,"uid":299514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"支支真係慘，小至一個app大至一個島都眼白白俾人搶走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500d47537dd4ad974f42d37e1394daf415757dc0","tid":2139740,"uid":337503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"借個位：<br />\n<br />\n繳請大家投個票：一句到尾，你支唔支持美國佬買Tiktok?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2139709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2139709</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}